{"tid":814172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賽跑冠軍🏃？老婦西環遭泥頭車撞　捲車底重傷死亡","createTime":"2018-09-11T04:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T14:12:52.000Z","uid":46896,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"576957fce57ff2efc5e5f887d6afaef7fa96d4a2","tid":814172,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"西環石山街近士美菲路發生交通意外，今早(11日)11時18分，一名87歲老婦在橫過馬路時遭一輛泥頭車撞及，捲入車底重傷，消防接報到場將老婦救出，但已陷入昏迷，立即由救護車送院搶救，惜告返魂乏術。警方正調查意外原因，現場留下一攤血漬，以及一塊鮮魚，懷疑老婦在買餸途中遇上意外。 <br />\n<br />\n受意外影響，士美菲路往薄扶林道方向近石山街的部分行車線現已封閉，交通受阻。"},{"pid":"8754df0ad878e7b2b9bbc956c503a954f5fd4057","tid":814172,"uid":121711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T05:39:28.000Z","msg":"我是七八十歲人 短跑的冠軍"},{"pid":"94d93da830102fe84e76997f8c8dd7009efff9aa","tid":814172,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"亂過馬路定泥頭車衝紅燈？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e210ce37dd0d73eeb320956dd14323c92fb6ff","tid":814172,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94d93da830102fe84e76997f8c8dd7009efff9aa","tid":814172,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"亂過馬路定泥頭車衝紅燈？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:54:49.000Z","msg":"why not both ?"},{"pid":"fbc6e403cc3283d04b2ee201fdca02719439fef3","tid":814172,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18e210ce37dd0d73eeb320956dd14323c92fb6ff","tid":814172,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94d93da830102fe84e76997f8c8dd7009efff9aa","tid":814172,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"亂過馬路定泥頭車衝紅燈？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T12:54:49.000Z","msg":"why not both ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20